        <title>Manifold Air Temperature (MAT) Sensor</title>
        <figure id="f2651015" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figJ09/J09016.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="240px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 365. MAT sensor</caption>
        </figure>
        <para>The MAT sensor, a thermistor sensor, detects intake manifold air temperature.</para>
        <para>The MAT signal is monitored by the ECM for EGR operation.</para>
        <para>The MAT sensor is installed in the right front of the intake manifold.</para>
